titles.title: Directing the Secretary of the Senate to make corrections in the enrollment of the bill S. 1312.

action.text: Mr. Williams asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Voice Vote.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 10/3/1994--Introduced. Directs the Secretary of the Senate to make corrections in the enrollment of S. 1312 (Pension Annuitants Protection Act of 1993).
